              "free_text": [
                " Two ionisation chambers: one Frisch-",
                " gridded for the forward detection of products (alpha",
                " and 9Be) with signal digitisation of the anode and",
                " cathode signals, the other without grid for backward",
                " detection of U(n,f) fission fragments.",
                "Gas mixture of krypton Kr(95%)CH4(5%) was used as",
                " detector medium.",
                "Forward IOCH:",
                " Diameter of electrodes    = 18 cm,",
                " Cathode-to-anode distance = 41 mm,",
                " Grid-to-anode distance    =  4 mm.",
                "Backward IOCH:",
